sketch.compiler.main.sten

Class StencilSmtSketchMain

  • java.lang.Object
    • SequentialSMTSketchMain
      • sketch.compiler.main.sten.StencilSmtSketchMain

  • public class StencilSmtSketchMain
extends SequentialSMTSketchMain
    Convert StreamIt programs to legal Java code. This is the main entry point for the StreamIt syntax converter. Running it as a standalone program reads the list of files provided on the command line and produces equivalent Java code on standard output or the file named in the --output command-line parameter.
